  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Technician (Home appliances)",
  "description": "<p>Our client is a leading player in <strong>Kitchen Appliance Industry.</strong> They are looking for a Service Technician to join their Team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located in the <strong>East area</strong> – easily accessible.<br /></p><p><strong>About The Role: </strong></p><ul><li>Basic + Variable Bonus + Phone Allowance + Transport Allowance + Service Commission + OT </li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide efficient after-sales technical support, including troubleshooting, maintenance, and installation of the company’s home kitchen products at customer locations island-wide.</li><li>Maintain adequate inventory of service and maintenance parts in the service vehicle.</li><li>Conduct basic user training and product usage guidance for customers.</li><li>Prepare, explain, and close after-service reports with customers.</li><li>Represent the company professionally as a frontline service representative.</li><li>Collaborate effectively with internal teams and external partners.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Nitec in Engineering or a related field</li><li>Minimum 1-2 years’ experience in servicing any home appliances</li><li>Must possess a Class 3 Driving License</li><li>Understand blue prints and drawings</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email Address: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R25157233</li><li>EA Personnel Name: Loh Pooi Keng</li></ul>",
